            <lg xml:id="TK67">
<l>tantai makaṟkāṟṟu naṉṟi yavaiyattu</l>
<l>munti yiruppac ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The [greatest] favor a father does his son is so to form him</l>
